<h2 id="address-layout">1. Setting up the address layout for delivery notes</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Setup » CRM » Address layout</strong> menu, you can individually set up address layouts for your countries of delivery for the order document <strong>Delivery note</strong>. The address layouts for the countries of delivery German, France and the United Kingdom are already available in your plentymarkets system by default. Proceed as described below to set up an address layout for delivery notes.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Setting up the address layout for delivery notes:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » CRM » Address layout</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>New layout</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus-square  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the desired settings. Note <a href="#table-set-up-address-layout">Table 1</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
