<p>Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span> and select a language version from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter translations for the name and description.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
