</table>
</div>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="delete-groups">6.4.4. Deleting groups again</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Previously created groups are displayed in the menu <strong>Setup » Settings » Properties » Groups</strong>.
Groups can also be deleted here.</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Select the groups (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-check-square  "></i></span>) that you want to delete.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-trash  "></i></span> in the upper left corner.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Confirm your decision.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: Properties that are assigned to groups remain unaffected.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="work-with-properties">6.5. Working with existing properties</h3>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="search-properties">6.5.1. Searching for properties</h4>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Searching for properties:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » Properties » Configuration</strong>.</p>
<div class="olist loweralpha">
<ol class="loweralpha" type="a">
<li>
<p><strong><em>Option 1</em></strong>: Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span> to see a list of all the properties.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong><em>Option 2</em></strong>: Click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-filter  "></i></span> to narrow down the search results with filters.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on a property in the search results to open a detailed view.
There you can modify the property’s settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
